    section.mission-section
        .content-wrap
            h2.mission-section__header.section-header Our Mission
            p.mission-section__copy
                | The St. John Educational Foundation works to further educational opportunities for underpriveleged Filipino students. The foundation was established on the basic principles of 
                span.emphasis love, giving, excellence,
                |  and 
                span.emphasis perseverance
                | . Members express their love and sense of giving to their community by contributing money, time, and effort to achieve the mission and objectives of the foundation. 
