            h2.goal-section__header.section-header Our Goals
            .goal-callout-container
                .goal-callout
                    .goal-callout__icon
                        img(src='img/icon-scholarship.svg')
                    .goal-callout__copy
                        | Providing a free scholarship program for both Filipino high school and college students

