                    .testimonial-carousel__hero
                        img(src='img/testimonial-1.png')

                    .testimonial-carousel__copy
                        | As a college student pursuing a Bachelor of Science in Agricultural Engineering at Isabella State University (Echague Campus), my goal is to finish my course in 5 years. Then I hope to pass the board examination.  I will find a job that fits my studies to repay the financial support that my alma mater (St. Johns Educational Foundation) have provided for me during my college years.

            a.testimonial-section__link-out(href='')
                | Read More Testimonials

    section.fundraiser-section
        .content-wrap
            .fundraiser-section__header.section-header The Annual Dinner Dance Fundraiser
            .fundraiser-section__hero
                img(src='img/fundraiser-hero.jpg')

            .fundraiser-section__copy
                | The benefactors of this foundation come from all over the world. We have members in many of the major cities of the U.S., members in Canada, and even some from Europe and the Middle East. Each year, since July of 2004, a dinner dance fundraiser has been held in a different host city to bring these members together.

